tags.name: Mt Cabot Trail
tags.note:
Western access to the Mt Cabot Trail is unclear and possibly prohibited, see https://www.vftt.org/forums/showthread.php?50910-The-Info-on-Mt-Cabot

To check current access status, contact the Androscoggin Ranger District at 1-603-466-2713.
